import * as react from 'react';
import {
  Stack,
  Grid,
  Table,
  TableBody,
  TableCell,
  TableContainer,
  TableHead,
  TableRow,
  Typography,
  Button,
} from '@mui/material';

const Alerts_Stat = [
  { label: 'Open', value: 1 },
  { label: 'Ack', value: 1 },
  { label: 'Resolved', value: 1 },
  { label: 'Total', value: 1 },
];

export default function Alerts() {
  return (
    <Grid
      container
      direction="column"
      spacing={2}
      sx={{ bgcolor: 'background.paper', minHeight: 0, flex: 1 }}
    >
      <Grid size={{ xs: 12, md: 12 }}>
        <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ flex: 1 }}>
          Alerts
        </Typography>
      </Grid>

      <Grid size={{ xs: 12, md: 12 }} sx={{ color: 'primary.main' }}>
        <Grid container>
          <Grid size={{ xs: 3, md: 3 }} sx={{ border: '1px solid', borderRadius: 2 }}>
            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ flex: 1 }}>
              Open:1
            </Typography>
          </Grid>
          <Grid size={{ xs: 3, md: 3 }}>
            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ flex: 1 }}>
              Ack:1
            </Typography>
          </Grid>
          <Grid size={{ xs: 3, md: 3 }}>
            <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ flex: 1 }}>
              Resolved:1
            </Typography>
          </Grid>
          <Grid size={{ xs: 3, md: 3 }} />
        </Grid>
        <Grid size={{ xs: 12, md: 12 }} sx={{ flex: 1, minHeight: 0 }}>
          <Stack direction="row" sx={{ flex: 1, minHeight: 0 }}></Stack>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Grid>
  );
}
